RelatedSentence: Military police and the military fire department were checking on a suspicious pacakage Monday morning near the Pearl Harbor Navy Exchange Monday morning , according to the city 's Traffic Management Center .
Police closed Bougainville Drive and parts of Radford Drive and Valkenburgh Drive .
The Traffic Management Center was reporting that the NEX was on lockdown .

The roads were reopened just after 8:30 a.m. Joint Base Security and explosive ordnance disposal personnel determined the suspicious object on the corner of Radford Drive and Bougainville Drive was not dangerous .
